sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway (Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant BFH as body-field-to-header<br/>(upstream plugin)
    participant MPR as model-provider-resolver<br/>plugin
    participant AT as api-translation<br/>plugin
    participant AKI as apikey-injection<br/>plugin
    participant NRG as nemo-request-guard<br/>plugin
    participant NRespG as nemo-response-guard<br/>plugin
    participant NeMo as NeMo Guardrails<br/>HTTP
    participant Provider as Model Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 1: External Model Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>BFH: gRPC ext_proc/9004<br/>Request body (plaintext)
    BFH->>BFH: Extract model name from body<br/>Set X-Gateway-Model-Name header

    BFH->>MPR: CycleState passthrough
    MPR->>MPR: Lookup ExternalModel in modelInfoStore<br/>Resolve provider name + model mapping
    Note right of MPR: Writes to CycleState:<br/>provider, model, credential ref

    MPR->>AT: CycleState with provider info
    AT->>AT: Translate request body<br/>OpenAI → provider-native format
    Note right of AT: OpenAI/Bedrock: path rewrite only<br/>Azure: path rewrite<br/>Anthropic: full body transform<br/>Vertex: path with project/location

    AT->>AKI: CycleState with translated body
    AKI->>AKI: Lookup API key in secretStore<br/>Inject auth header per provider
    Note right of AKI: OpenAI: Authorization Bearer<br/>Anthropic: x-api-key<br/>Azure: api-key header

    opt NeMo Guardrails Enabled
        AKI->>NRG: CycleState passthrough
        NRG->>NeMo: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP, input content
        NeMo-->>NRG: 200 OK, status: allowed/blocked
        alt Request Blocked
            NRG-->>Gateway: 403 Forbidden
            Gateway-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
        end
    end

    Gateway->>Provider: Translated request<br/>HTTPS/443, API key header
    Provider-->>Gateway: Model response<br/>HTTPS/443

    opt NeMo Response Guard Enabled
        Gateway->>NRespG: gRPC ext_proc/9004<br/>Response body
        NRespG->>NeMo: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP, output content
        NeMo-->>NRespG: 200 OK, status: allowed/blocked
        alt Response Blocked
            NRespG-->>Gateway: Modified response (blocked)
        end
    end

    AT->>AT: Translate response body<br/>provider-native → OpenAI format
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 2: ExternalModel & Secret Reconciliation (Background)

    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    loop ExternalModel Watch
        MPR->>K8sAPI: Watch ExternalModel CRDs<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>MPR: ExternalModel events
        MPR->>MPR: Update modelInfoStore
    end

    loop Secret Watch
        AKI->>K8sAPI: Watch Secrets (bbr-managed=true)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>AKI: Secret events
        AKI->>AKI: Update secretStore
    end
